1. Create RDS instance
   Engine        : PostgreSQL 15
   Instance type : db.t3.micro
   VPC           : same as your EKS cluster
   DB name       : ecommerce
   Username      : ecommerce
   Password      : choose a strong password

2. Security group on RDS
   Inbound rule:
   Type     : PostgreSQL
   Port     : 5432
   Source   : EKS node group security group ID

3. Note the RDS endpoint
   Format: xxx.xxxxxxxx.ap-south-1.rds.amazonaws.com
